These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
There 2 different types of food: cranberry, cucumber
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
City: marseilles, liverpool
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the person eating cucumber is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Food   | cucumber     | cranberry   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| City     | marseilles | liverpool    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, cabbage
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, documentary
House: modern, art-deco
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, dunhill
1. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching action movies is the dunhill-smoker##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  |
| House           | art-deco         | modern     |
| Cigar     | bluemaster   | dunhill    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: woodworking, singing
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
City: hannover, berlin
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Hobby    | singing     | woodworking |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| City         | hannover         | berlin        |
| Transport   | bike         | helicopter    |

