.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, handball
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, turtle
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, cooking
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, pop
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
3. the fan of pop is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Sport      | handball     | parkour |
| Pet          | turtle   | rabbit  |
| Hobby         | card-games | cooking     |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | pop         |

