2 different games are played: canasta, backgammon
There are 2 different nationalities: french, thai
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, basketball
1. the thai is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the project-manager is in an even position##4
4. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
| Job           | accountant | project-manager |
| Game   | canasta    | backgammon      |
| Nationality           | french      | thai          |
| Sport         | basketball | badminton       |

