3. the person traveling to new-york is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Sport         | skateboarding        | ice-hockey |
| Pet         | frog          | goat     |
| City   | new-york        | marseilles     |

 